name: Sin Collector
description: "She collects the sins of humankind and gives nothing in return ..." they cried. Fools. What did they expect ?  Limited digital collection of an original traditional charcoal drawing made by Sedas.  Part of the art series 'Digital Waves' regarding the impact of technology on humanity. More info - see our website at https://en.sedas.be/art-series/digital-waves/
